  <body>
    <div id="hero">
      <br />
      <%- include("header.ejs") %>
      <%- include("nav.ejs") %>

      <h1>Global Flavors Delivered to Your Kitchen</h1>
    </div>
    <div id="searchHere">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif;">Search Recipes</h2>
      <form id="inner" action="/search" method="POST">
        <input
          type="text"
          name="searchRecipe"
          placeholder="e.g japanese"
          style="height: 3rem; padding: 1rem; width: 85%; border-radius: 9px"
        />
        <button
          type="submit"
          style="border: none; height: 3rem; width: 13%; border-radius: 9px"
        >
          <img
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/icons/search.svg"
            alt="search icon"
            style="height: 50%"
          />
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="happy">
        <a href="/cake">
        <button>
          <div class="card-img-top CheeseCake" style="display: flex">
            <div class="food"><h3>Cheese Cake</h3></div>
          </div>
        </button>
        </a>
        <a href="/japanese">
        <button>
          <div class="card-img-top japanese" style="display: flex">
            <div class="food"><h3>Japanese</h3></div>
          </div>
        </button>
        </a>

        <a href="/italian">
        <button>
          <div class="card-img-top italian" style="display: flex">
            <div class="food"><h3>Italian</h3></div>
          </div>
        </button>
        </a>

        <a href="/diet">
        <button>
          <div class="card-img-top diet" style="display: flex">
            <div class="food"><h3>Diet</h3></div>
          </div>
        </button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="about">
      <div class="aboutMe">
        <div class="mypic">
          <img src="myPic.jpeg" alt="My Picture" id="myImg" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>About Me</h2>
          <br /><br />
          <p id="para">
            Hi! I’m Khushie  — recipe explorer, and occasional
            kitchen chaos survivor . When I’m not drooling over delicious
            creations online, I’m hunting for tasty recipes, testing new flavors
            (sometimes successfully!), and sharing them here on Recipe Hub. I
            started this blog to make finding fun, easy, and yummy recipes a
            breeze. My goal? To make cooking exciting, not stressful, and help
            you discover new dishes without the hassle. I love music, a little
            dancing in the kitchen, and being the ultimate “taste tester” (even
            if it’s just for fun ). So welcome to Recipe Hub — where cooking
            is enjoyable, mistakes are allowed, and dessert always comes first!
            
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%- include("footer.ejs") %>
  </body>
</html>
